    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >BUILD SCRAP is a roguelike deckbuilding strategy game where you move across a grid-based map and battle enemies using customizable cards. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041130/extras/d491c91eb923417900010112c0b283e0.poster.avif?t=1754614261\" width=526 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041130/extras/d491c91eb923417900010112c0b283e0.webm?t=1754614261\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041130/extras/d491c91eb923417900010112c0b283e0.mp4?t=1754614261\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether attacking, avoiding, or defending, sometimes you can use your enemies to take advantage of the stage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041130/extras/a7cba3cb24a0fef8cb3e18136ee9360a.poster.avif?t=1754614261\" width=526 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041130/extras/a7cba3cb24a0fef8cb3e18136ee9360a.webm?t=1754614261\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041130/extras/a7cba3cb24a0fef8cb3e18136ee9360a.mp4?t=1754614261\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041130/extras/7ec03ef32a2b48e3d2e08eefa82f5d68.avif?t=1754614261\" width=526 height=296 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can customize the performance of your cards by synthesizing marks on them, allowing you to fight with your own unique cards and your own unique strategy. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get through various situations created by unique enemies. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041130/extras/898f31881369e1a311f9e49d126e16ad.avif?t=1754614261\" width=526 height=296 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041130/extras/1d099c1643abb5991b79bfe2809f9091.avif?t=1754614261\" width=526 height=296 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041130/extras/f4132f91ecb1c0eb6d3b3a23bbb19b20.avif?t=1754614261\" width=526 height=290 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041130/extras/4c56400c9ec8eba7008d5edb15c3937b.avif?t=1754614261\" width=526 height=296 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041130/extras/f2c926ca60a2af7645917aa96e16999a.avif?t=1754614261\" width=526 height=288 /></span></p>",
